com.serena.dmclient.api
Class SystemAttributes

java.lang.Object
  com.serena.dmclient.api.SystemAttributes

public class SystemAttributes
extends java.lang.Object

This class provides constants for all system attributes to be queried on certain objects. The object(s) for which a certain system attribute can be queried, can be found in brackets on each attribute definition.
Constants are provided for the following objects: Request, ItemRevision, RequestAttachment, Project, Baseline, User, Part The actual numbers may change in a future release, although the symbol names will stay the same unless documented otherwise.
